{"tid":369354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有小小掛住娛樂百分百。。","createTime":"2017-08-22T09:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T14:06:07.000Z","uid":82917,"like":41,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe25b46a68ec67cae02e2335fd54d64591a1aa5","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人係長期娛百fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係由小豬小鬼搭檔個陣開始追<br />\n以前放學返黎就即刻上youtube睇前一日個集<br />\n<br />\n羅志祥同黃鴻升個種火花真係同歷代主持黎比係無人能及<br />\n全盛期2008-2011 個陣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/170958_af4b7ae20e91b286041b956606555752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F170958_af4b7ae20e91b286041b956606555752.jpg&h=0c19b727&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/171002_71268fc79a2786e96c9fed0bf03d9929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F171002_71268fc79a2786e96c9fed0bf03d9929.jpg&h=20b9026b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/171003_09c6ae0423a6935508f236e0c3c78e02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F171003_09c6ae0423a6935508f236e0c3c78e02.jpg&h=a760c1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論係live鳩up定預錄有嘉賓個啲都係咁撚搞笑<br />\n同埋 瘋狂開黃腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家youtube啲片都比人del哂了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前細個睇下笑下咁又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家羅又奶共 拍個套乜撚極限挑戰做小丑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用不著吧 以佢咁既地位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃好似摺摺地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢退左娛百之後就冇乜點聽過佢個朵了。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢兩個昔日好兄弟搞成咁 真是唏噓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩既，有邊個甘心比人踩住一世，永遠做細個個呀。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好掛住娛百呀。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c0392745f5ed8d678d1f69c7e6a7c93f94a55d","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee0d2f99d1b73b6fc3aa77610868ed2caf3a393","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"難道我老了？"},{"pid":"30f8dc1ddb00aae0953fc7076a919b27989d7692","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"冇人識娛百？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bbf05c637eead773065f4148d7e698688cf43b","tid":369354,"uid":51453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁你想點"},{"pid":"c911f360905821d0a5b5c4238773de7c6846e698","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你想點</blockquote><br />\n一齊重溫囉。。"},{"pid":"650f81519f1d26d45506f048ebeab23cb7299e9a","tid":369354,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"時代的眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdce1582d2c98b8b60ba7ca54892dd4dc23305c0","tid":369354,"uid":65756,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:19:33.000Z"